# Security Policy

## Supported Versions

Currently, until further notice, all versions of Scarlet are classed under the Vulnerability Assessment Support (VAS for short).
This means that any and all reports for Security issues will be received and analysed, and patched (where applicable).

| Version | Supported          |
| ------- | ------------------ |
| x.x.x (all)  | :white_check_mark: |

## Reporting a Vulnerability

If you have found an exploit (of any severity) for the API, AI, or Wrappers, then please open an issue using the `Security Report` template.
Filing this report will ensure the issue gets the appropriate attention it deserves
